llow user to register and examine a list of targets using DES images. User can sort and filter lists. Targets are organized in classes of objects, like: Galaxy Clusters, Strong Lensing, QSOs, outliers, etc.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Target list level operations:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Add/delete target lists\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Favorite a target list to easily navigate through the lists\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Search target list by name</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Target level operations (left side) :</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage target list content is displayed (e.g. sort columns, lock columns, hide columns)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create, save, copy and delete a Target List selection filter (e.g. high-z massive clusters)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manipulate Target List items (e.g. rank, reject, and filter)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Comment Target List items </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Generate and display target list in mosaics in PNG formats  and send e-mail notification to user\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow the deletion of the mosaic files</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow Target List download. Link is sent via e-mail to user\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow Save As of the new target list and send notification to the user\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow association between columns of uploaded file and Unified Content Descriptor, for standard analysis of list</span>\r\n\r\n<b>At the image level (right side) :</b><b>\r\n</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">VisiOmatic tool is used to display the image\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Display image (element of the target list attached to a tile)</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank and reject images\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Add comment to object and position</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Display System and Object Explorer (informations and plots about system or object)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crop and download image</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Image display options (show/hide comments, show/hide crosshair, show/hide System Members, etc.)</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">VisiOmatic native features: catalog overlay, image levels, layers, etc.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Target Viewer','https://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu/target/','publish','closed','closed','','target-viewer','','','2019-02-04 14:24:11','2019-02-04 16:24:11','',0,'http://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu//?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2017-06-06 15:30:01','2017-06-06 18:30:01','','science_products_200x200','','inherit','open','closed','','science_products_200x200','','','2017-06-06 15:30:01','2017-06-06 18:30:01','',10,'http://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu//wp-content/uploads/2017/06/science_products_200x200.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(12,1,'2017-06-06 15:30:02','2017-06-06 18:30:02','','target_viewer_200x200','','inherit','open','closed','','target_viewer_200x200','','','2017-06-06 15:30:02','2017-06-06 18:30:02','',10,'http://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu//wp-content/uploads/2017/06/target_viewer_200x200.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(13,1,'2017-06-06 15:30:11','2017-06-06 18:30:11','[embed]https://youtu.be/osiGRNlMIT0[/embed]\r\n<p class=\"app-paragrafo1\">Manage lists of targets with image display, cutouts, ranking and reject functionalities. <a href=\"http://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu/dri/apps/target\" target=\"_self\">click here</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"app-paragrafo2\">The main functionalities of the Target vi