 overlay of tile grid and objects <a href=\"http://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu/dri/apps/sky/\" target=\"_self\">click here</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"app-paragrafo2\">The main functionalities are:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Footprint</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"app-paragrafo2\">\r\n 	<li>All-sky visualization in spherical projection</li>\r\n 	<li>grizY and RGB HiPS images for DES releases</li>\r\n 	<li>HiPS images from other suverys like 2MASS, WISE, DSS, SDSS9 as well as extinction and Halpha maps for comparions</li>\r\n 	<li>Visualization of HEALPIX maps</li>\r\n 	<li>Hierarchical overlay of objects</li>\r\n 	<li>Overlay of polygons like DES footprint, tile grid CCDs and healpix grid</li>\r\n 	<li>Search by RA, Dec or tilename</li>\r\n 	<li>Direct link to specific RA, Dec position specified in the URL</li>\r\n 	<li>Export the current view to PNG</li>\r\n 	<li>Access to Tile Viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Mosaic</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"app-paragrafo2\">\r\n 	<li>Mosaic of thumbnails (400 x 400 pixels) for each tile in grizY and RGB for rapid evaluation of features in the co-add images</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to flag a tile</li>\r\n 	<li>Link to the Tile Viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Tile List</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"app-paragrafo2\">\r\n 	<li>Information for each tile like Tilename, RA, Dec, l, b, and Dataset in a searchable and sortable table</li>\r\n 	<li>Link to the Tile Viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Available Videos</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sky Viewer adjustments</li>\r\n 	<li>Sky Viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[huge_it_videogallery id=\"2\"]','Sky Viewer','http://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu:8080/dri/apps/sky/','inherit','closed','closed','','6-autosave-v1','','','2017-09-01 17:33:20','2017-09-01 20:33:20','',6,'http://desportal.cosmology.illinois.edu//6-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(43,1,'2017-07-12 17:02:21','2017-07-12 20:02:21','[embed]https://youtu.be/n6POra35pwc[/embed]\r\n<p class=\"app-paragrafo1\">All-sky visualization of DES releases in grizY and RGB with overlay of ti