ve:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow user to register and examine a list of targets using DES images. User can sort and filter lists. Targets are organized in classes of objects, like: Galaxy Clusters, Strong Lensing, QSOs, outliers, etc.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Target list level operations:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Add/delete target lists\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Favorite a target list to easily navigate through the lists\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Search target list by name</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Target level operations (left side) :</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage target list content is displayed (e.g. sort columns, lock columns, hide columns)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create, save, copy and delete a Target List selection filter (e.g. high-z massive clusters)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manipulate Target List items (e.g. rank, reject, and filter)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Comment Target List items </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Generate and display target list in mosaics in PNG formats  and send e-mail notification to user\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow the deletion of the mosaic files</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow Target List download. Link is sent via e-mail to user\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow Save As of the new target list and send notification to the user\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allow association between columns of uploaded file and Unified Content Descriptor, for standard analysis of list</span>\r\n\r\n<b>At the image level (right side) :</b><b>\r\n</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">VisiOmatic tool is used to display the image\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Display image (element of the target list attached to a tile)</span><span 